in Hong Kong?

832
01:27:05,877 --> 01:27:07,777
You knew that l came back
to Saigon with Mun,

833
01:27:07,846 --> 01:27:10,679
so why did you only want
to see him?

834
01:27:10,782 --> 01:27:12,249
You have so many secrets.

835
01:27:12,350 --> 01:27:15,114
What else haven't you told
me?

836
01:27:18,390 --> 01:27:20,984
l have nothing to explain.

837
01:27:21,226 --> 01:27:23,820
lf you say l'm wrong then
l'm wrong.

838
01:27:23,928 --> 01:27:25,520
l've never regretted
anything.

839
