843
01:27:51,289 --> 01:27:54,816
How many will you kill
before you're happy?

844
01:27:56,628 --> 01:27:59,791
There's no reason behind our
actions.

845
01:27:59,931 --> 01:28:02,092
Who is right, who is wrong,

846
01:28:02,233 --> 01:28:05,134
someday you'll understand.

847
01:28:08,406 --> 01:28:11,239
When Mun came,

848
01:28:11,376 --> 01:28:14,436
