it means death.

851
01:28:19,584 --> 01:28:22,052
He said that you'd never
betray me.

852
01:28:22,187 --> 01:28:26,647
But now l know what kind
of a person you are.

853
01:28:30,862 --> 01:28:34,730
Even if you aren't my enemy,

854
01:28:34,833 --> 01:28:38,234
l never want to see you
again as long as l live.

855
01:28:38,269 --> 01:28:39,099
Mark

856
01:28:39,170 --> 01:28:40,432
Mark

857
01:30:19,704 --> 01:30:21,831
Mark

858
01:30:27,912 --> 01:30:29,709
Mun isn't dead He's over
there Hurry

859
01:30:29,847 --> 01:30:31,109
Hurry

860
01:30:37,622 --> 01:30:38,714
Mun

861
01:30:41,526 --> 01:30:42,288
Mun

862
01:30:42,393 --> 01:30:43,223
Mark

863
01:30:45,663 --> 01:30:46,789
Mun

864
01:30:48,066 --> 01:30:50,261
Have you seen Kit?

865
01:30:50,435 --> 01:30:55,134
Where's Kit? Why isn't she
with you?

866
01:30:55,406 --> 01:30:56,430
Kit?

867
