killing for.

879
01:33:10,875 --> 01:33:13,070
Miss Chow, don't move

880
01:33:13,211 --> 01:33:15,645
Put your gun down

881
01:34:04,562 --> 01:34:07,929
At times like this l realize
how much we need each other.

882
