When you die, l want you to
know who killed you.

898
01:36:29,473 --> 01:36:31,338
Even God will not care.

899
01:36:31,375 --> 01:36:34,776
A man is responsible for his
own actions.

900
01:36:34,812 --> 01:36:37,246
lt's becoming a slaughter-
house out there.

901
01:36:37,281 --> 01:36:39,442
