lt makes no difference if l
live or die.

907
01:36:58,269 --> 01:37:02,399
l just want to see blood
debts paid in blood.

908
01:37:05,142 --> 01:37:07,372
You've a just a garage
mechanic

909
01:37:07,545 --> 01:37:09,445
Remember,

910
01:37:09,580 --> 01:37:12,913
what goes around, comes
around.

911
01:37:13,017 --> 01:37:15,042
You'll get what you deserve

912
01:37:23,694 --> 01:37:27,130
My gun is already out of
bullets.

913
01:37:27,198 --> 01:37:30,190
You have your chance.

914
01:38:07,405 --> 01:38:10,704
Don't shoot

915
01:38:33,264 --> 01:38:34,390
Kit

