l'm going now.

932
01:41:21,365 --> 01:41:25,199
Don't let Kit follow me.

933
01:41:25,836 --> 01:41:27,667
Wait

934
01:42:57,394 --> 01:42:58,952
Mun

935
01:43:24,688 --> 01:43:26,952
Mun, get in

936
01:44:13,237 --> 01:44:14,465
Mun

937
